7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Retina 既不是指分辨率，也不是单独指 PPI，而是指视觉效果。我们一般称 [[devicePixelRatio]] 大于或等于 <em><strong>2</strong></em> 的屏幕为 Retina 屏幕 (r 屏)，否则为 非 r 屏。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"Retina-的原理\"><a href=\"#Retina-的原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Retina 的原理\"></a>Retina 的原理</h1><p>受 windows 操作系统的影响，多数人心中会产生这样的逻辑：分辨率越高，字会显得越小。这是因为整个屏幕的面积主要由像素面积构成，即在相同面积下，分辨率越高，像素数量也越多，单个像素的面积也一定越小。于是高分辨率就对应着小像素，而像素小，则由像素构成的文字就小。所以就有了『分辨率越高，字会显得越小』的印象。</p>\n<p>这是因为操作系统的 HiDPI 渲染方式，它决定了一个文字或图标最终以多少个像素来表达。2 倍 r 屏它在表达屏幕上每个元素时，都使用了 4 倍于非 r 屏的像素个数。这样算下来，像素尺寸为 1&#x2F;4，像素数目为 4 倍，于是最终渲染出来的文字和图标的大小与非 r 屏的相当。</p>\n","text":"概述 Retina 既不是指分辨率，也不是单独指 PPI，而是指视觉效果。我们一般称 [[devicePixelRatio]] 大于或等于 2 的屏幕为 Retina 屏幕 (r 屏)，否则为 非 r 屏。 Retina 的原理受 windows 操作系统的影响，多数人心中会产生...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":421,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">概述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Retina-%E7%9A%84%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Retina 的原理</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Devmacy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/24/pSYhwB4.jpg","link":"/","description":"数字花园","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Devmacy","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"SASS","uid":"883d8fc4b0b2c186df3a69be746acff8","slug":"SASS","date":"2023-07-07T17:47:16.091Z","updated":"2023-07-07T17:47:16.242Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/SASS.json","keywords":"Digital Garden","cover":null,"text":"","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":0,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Devmacy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2023/01/24/pSYhwB4.jpg","link":"/","description":"数字花园","socials":{"github"